1012
01:00:16.742 --> 01:00:18.572
Now, for minimal residual disease detection,

1013
01:00:19.682 --> 01:00:23.582
assay technology can partly overcome insufficient ctDNA, as we've

1014
01:00:23.622 --> 01:00:27.542
