1015
01:00:27.582 --> 01:00:27.942
of blood.

1016
01:00:28.862 --> 01:00:32.402
And there are now many great MRD assays, a subset listed

1017
01:00:32.442 --> 01:00:36.242
here, spanning tumor-informed bespoke, tumor-informed non-bespoke, tumor

