01:01:01.222 --> 01:01:04.182
and it's due to the biology. There are biological limitations that constrain

1026
01:01:04.202 --> 01:01:04.722
detection.

1027
01:01:06.102 --> 01:01:10.082
In addition, beyond simply detecting MRD, we want to be able to profile

1028
01:01:10.122 --> 01:01:14.062
it to inform therapy selection, what to target when the cancer is coming back.

1029
01:01:14.112 --> 01:01:18.002
And when the cancer is coming back, there's not yet a lesion that you can go and

