01:01:18.222 --> 01:01:21.221
biopsy. So how do we get this information in?

1031
01:01:21.382 --> 01:01:25.342
And that's where to date, comprehensive genomic profiling tests are largely

1032
01:01:25.402 --> 01:01:29.052
used in advanced cancer, but we want to push those into

