01:01:29.062 --> 01:01:31.582
earlier stages and really be able to profile

1034
01:01:31.702 --> 01:01:35.738
MRD.Now,

1035
01:01:35.758 --> 01:01:39.118
there's a lot to be excited about, a lot of great data,

