1068
01:03:34.438 --> 01:03:36.658
And it's basically a sampling probability.

1069
01:03:37.348 --> 01:03:41.018
It's what's the lowest fraction of ctDNA in the body, in the

1070
01:03:41.058 --> 01:03:44.698
