1084
01:04:31.438 --> 01:04:32.878
to call MRD,

1085
01:04:33.818 --> 01:04:37.698
the LoD95 with a binomial model would actually be 16 parts per million under

1086
01:04:37.758 --> 01:04:38.658
those circumstances.

1087
01:04:39.918 --> 01:04:43.317
But another critical parameter is the background error rate for the markers being

1088
01:04:43.378 --> 01:04:46.998
